{
  "texts": [
    "Two components comprise this strategy:(i) a strategy of learning multiple tasks simultaneously and, (ii) an advanced model that integrates discriminative and generative abilities using deep convolutional networks.",
    "Since the developed model links feature extraction and classification, it performs better than other generative models.",
    "It has a 95.04% accuracy rate.",
    "Another critical element is the use of multitask learning to overcome overfitting.",
    "The use of regularization instead of other data types proves the uniqueness of the model."
  ]
}